FBIS4-64588 "drweu087_j_94008" FBIS-WEU-94-087 Daily Report 4 May 1994 ITALY & VATICAN CITY Scalfaro Meets Kurdish Leader Talabani Scalfaro Meets Kurdish Leader Talabani BR0505080094 Rome LA REPUBBLICA in Italian 4 May 94 p 2 BR0505080094 Rome LA REPUBBLICA Italian BFN [Unattributed report: "Scalfaro Meets With Kurdish Talabani, One of Saddam's Rivals"] [Text] President Scalfaro received Jalal Talabani, leader of the Patriotic Union of Kurdistan and member of the Iraqi National Assembly, the front opposing Saddam Husayn's regime, at the Quirinale [president's palace] yesterday. Italy has a group of UN observers on Kurdish territory in northern Iraq, where there recently have been attacks against international obervers attributed to Baghdad's secret services. A group of British scientists has claimed that Saddam already has destroyed more than half the marshes in southern Iraq.
